You use a HashMap or HashSet to quickly check:

âœ… If a number exists

ğŸ§® How many times it occurs

ğŸ¯ If two numbers add up to a target

ğŸ§© Why Use Hashing?
âœ… Fast lookup in O(1) time
âœ… Store frequencies or indexes
