âœ… Used in: Two Sum, Frequency count, Longest subarrays, Anagrams

ğŸ’¡ Real-Life Analogy:
Think of HashMap as a magical cabinet ğŸ—„ï¸
You can write a label (key) and quickly find its contents (value)! ğŸ”‘

